name: Google Account Sites Login - Grey & Green (Dark)
description:
This is a dark style for the Google Login Screens.
Since they all use very similar pages, this is a general style for all of them. I included specific logos for Gmail and Voice. If there's space in the style, I might add logos for other sites in the future.
This style was a part of style 17417 but I separated them so we can use either.

2011 09 29 - Updated for new global login screens, combined logo from Voice. Moved logo.
2009 11 15 - Included style for logout screen as well.
2009 12 29 - Replaced logo
